## Hints for Future Agents
- CODEOWNERS is last-match-wins: a single file matches exactly ONE rule (the
  last one listed that matches). Ordering is load-bearing here. If you add a
  more-specific weave/ subtree rule, place it AFTER /weave/ or weave-sdk will
  silently re-own it.
